---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<Layout title="关于我们 - 立刷POS" currentPath="/about" description="了解立刷POS机 - 嘉联支付旗下品牌，持牌支付机构，致力于为小微商户提供安全合规的支付解决方案。500万+商户的选择，覆盖300+城市。" keywords="立刷POS,关于立刷,嘉联支付,POS机品牌,支付公司">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="relative bg-blue-600 text-white py-20 md:py-28 overflow-hidden">
		<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -translate-y-12 translate-x-1/3 w-[420px] h-[420px] bg-blue-400 rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
		<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 translate-y-1/3 -translate-x-1/4 w-[320px] h-[320px] bg-blue-500 rounded-full blur-[110px] opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
		<div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center drop-shadow-md">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6 tracking-tight">让支付更简单，让商业更高效</h1>
			<p class="text-xl text-gray-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-medium">立刷POS，致力于为千万小微商户提供安全、便捷的综合支付解决方案。</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-6">
		<Breadcrumbs items={[{label: '关于我们'}]} />
	</div>

	<!-- 公司介绍 -->
	<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">关于立刷</h2>
					<div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600">
						<p>立刷是国内领先的第三方支付品牌，专注于为小微商户、个人从业者提供一站式的收单服务。我们依托强大的技术实力和丰富的行业经验，不断推出符合市场需求的创新型智能支付终端。</p>
						<p>自成立以来，立刷始终秉承"安全、便捷、高效"的服务理念。我们不仅提供硬件设备，更致力于通过支付连接商业生态，为商户提供数据分析、会员管理等增值服务，助力商户数字化转型。</p>
						<p>如今，立刷已服务数百万商户，业务覆盖全国各地。我们将继续坚持以客户为中心，不断创新，为广大商户创造更多价值。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
					<div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl text-center flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
						<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">500万+</div>
						<div class="text-gray-600 font-medium">服务商户</div>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl text-center flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
						<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">100%</div>
						<div class="text-gray-600 font-medium">安全保障</div>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl text-center flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
						<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">365天</div>
						<div class="text-gray-600 font-medium">贴心服务</div>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl text-center flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
						<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">300+</div>
						<div class="text-gray-600 font-medium">覆盖城市</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- 核心优势 -->
	<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gray-50">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">我们的核心优势</h2>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-500">选择立刷，选择安心与省心</p>
			</div>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">极致安全</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">拥有央行颁发的支付牌照，多重加密技术保障资金与数据安全，让您收款无忧。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">极速到账</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">支持全年365天全天候交易，资金极速结算，有效提高您的资金流转效率。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">贴心服务</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">提供7x24小时专业客服支持，一对一解决您在使用过程中遇到的各类问题。</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">品牌价值观</h2>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-500">以安全为底线，以服务为核心，以长期合作为目标</p>
			</div>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div class="rounded-2xl border border-blue-50 bg-blue-50/60 p-8">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">安全第一</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">围绕支付安全、商户合规和设备稳定性构建服务标准，让每一次交易更放心。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-2xl border border-blue-50 bg-blue-50/60 p-8">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">客户为先</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">坚持需求导向，根据商户体量、行业特征和经营方式匹配更合适的支付方案。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-2xl border border-blue-50 bg-blue-50/60 p-8">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">持续赋能</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">不仅提供终端设备，更持续输出培训、售后与活动支持，帮助商户稳步经营。</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-center">
				<div>
					<div class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-5">服务流程</div>
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-5">从咨询到长期运营支持，全程有人跟进</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
						立刷重视商户服务体验，通过规范流程和专属顾问机制，帮助商户降低使用门槛，提升设备使用效率。
					</p>
					<div class="space-y-4">
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-50">
							<div class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">01 需求调研</div>
							<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">沟通商户行业属性、交易场景和日常收款结构。</p>
						</div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-50">
							<div class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">02 方案匹配</div>
							<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">依据门店经营模式选择终端型号、收款方式和服务组合。</p>
						</div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-50">
							<div class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">03 装机培训</div>
							<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">指导激活、交易测试、签购单和常见操作流程。</p>
						</div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-50">
							<div class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">04 售后跟进</div>
							<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">持续解决设备、结算、活动和日常使用中的问题。</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm border border-blue-50">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">服务承诺</h3>
					<div class="space-y-5">
						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<div class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">响应及时</div>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">常见咨询与售后问题快速响应，尽量减少商户经营中断。</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<div class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">方案稳妥</div>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">结合业务规模和行业特点推荐设备，避免盲目装机和资源浪费。</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<div class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">长期陪跑</div>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">围绕活动、运营和设备使用持续提供支持，帮助商户稳定增长。</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-20 bg-blue-600">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-5">成为立刷商户，享受专业服务</h2>
			<p class="text-blue-100 text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">从装机到售后，全程有专人跟进，让您专注经营。</p>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
				<a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-bold text-lg transition-colors shadow-lg">免费申请</a>
				<a href="tel:400-926-6655" class="border border-white/50 text-white hover:bg-white/10 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-bold text-lg transition-colors">400-926-6655</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
